                  </persName>
               
            , were indicted; the first for <rs id="t17710410-29-off154" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17710410-29-off154" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17710410-29-off154" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               the wilful murder of 
                     
